<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Shinobi Open-Source Academy</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #171717;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #0d1b60;
      padding: 24px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .logo {
      max-width: 180px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }

    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #304ffe;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .main-heading {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #171717;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .info-box {
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }

    .info-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .info-label {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #9e9e9e;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-right: 15px;
    }

    .info-value {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #171717;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: right;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .github-invite-box {
      background-color: #0d1b60;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .github-invite-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .github-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      margin-right: 12px;
    }

    .github-invite-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .github-invite-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .github-invite-action {
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    }

    .github-invite-action strong {
      color: #58a6ff;
    }

    .communities-list {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #304ffe;
      text-transform: capitalize;
    }

    .cta-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 35px 0;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: transparent !important;
      color: #304ffe !important;
      text-decoration: none !important;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      border: 2px solid #304ffe;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #304ffe !important;
      color: #ffffff !important;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      padding: 25px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }

    .footer-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9e9e9e;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .social-links {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .social-links a {
      color: #304ffe;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .contact-info {
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #9e9e9e;
    }

    .contact-info a {
      color: #304ffe;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="cid:logo" alt="Shinobi Open-Source Academy" class="logo">
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="greeting">Hi {{name}},</div>

      <div class="main-heading">Welcome to <strong>Shinobi Open-Source Academy</strong></div>

      <p>Thank you for joining our community. Your registration has been successfully processed and you're now part of
        our developer community.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-label">Member</div>
          <div class="info-value">{{name}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-label">Communities</div>
          <div class="info-value">
            <span class="communities-list">{{communities}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-label">Registration Date</div>
          <div class="info-value">{{date}}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-label">Status</div>
          <div class="info-value">Active</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="github-invite-box">
        <div class="github-invite-header">
          <svg class="github-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
            <path
              d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z" />
          </svg>
          <h3 class="github-invite-title">GitHub Organization Invitation Sent!</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="github-invite-text">
          We've sent you an invitation to join the <strong>Shinobi Open-Source Academy</strong> GitHub organization.
          This gives you access to our open-source projects, collaborative repositories, and community codebases.
        </p>
        <p class="github-invite-action">
          <strong>Check your email</strong> or <strong>GitHub notifications</strong> to accept the invitation and start
          contributing!
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>At Shinobi Open-Source Academy, we focus on practical learning through real-world projects and peer
        collaboration. Our communities provide structured learning paths, mentorship opportunities, and hands-on
        experience with modern development practices.</p>

      <p><strong>What to expect:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Weekly community meetings and technical discussions</li>
        <li>Project collaboration opportunities with other developers</li>
        <li>Access to learning resources and documentation</li>
        <li>Mentorship from experienced developers in your chosen communities</li>
        <li>Networking opportunities with like-minded professionals</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Important:</strong> You'll receive community meeting invitations and general updates every Monday.
        Please ensure your email notifications are enabled to stay informed about upcoming events and opportunities.</p>

      <div class="cta-section">
        <a href="https://shinobi-open-source.academy/#about" class="cta-button">Learn More About Us</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <p>Questions? Contact us at <a
            href="mailto:contact@shinobi-open-source.academy">contact@shinobi-open-source.academy</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-text">Â© {{currentYear}} Shinobi Open-Source Academy. All rights reserved.</div>
      <div class="footer-text">You're receiving this email because you registered at Shinobi Open-Source Academy.</div>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/Shinobi-Open-Source-Academy">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/SOSAcademy_">X (Twitter)</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/shinobi-open-source-academy/">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/X9PWySkvKM">Discord</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
